data.name: Cinnamon
data.description: Rajput architecture, magnificence and sumptuousness - this is the essence that pervades Cinnamon, originally the erstwhile dining room of the Prime Minister of Jaipur State Cinnamon is a gourmet theatre endearing the many faces of Indian cuisine from four Princely States of India – Rajputana, Awadh, Hyderabad and Kashmir. The restaurant showcases the true worth of our love for the age old culinary art through its contemporary styling and artistic ways. It was an instinct to discover the pleasure of creating perfection that drove us to a yearning to put together a repertoire of simple dishes to give us a place on the global culinary map. The journey takes a swirl through the “Bajot”, a unique private dining area in the restaurant, wherein our esteemed guests are treated to a special chef’s menu, pampered by our highly trained servers and chef-in-charge himself. The menu showcases dishes made to order and proves to be a boon for connoisseurs of food. Redefining Indian food, decor and the service a class apart, our menu uses the freshest of ingredients, authentic herbs and whole spices to create a modest twist in the traditional cuisines from the Princely States of India. Allow us to use a teaspoon of cinnamon or a strand of saffron or slivers of almonds and pistachio to entice you and delight you with wisps of the aromas from the different regions of India. We trust you will enjoy the experience and explore your gourmet senses. So pamper your taste buds and relish the ever enthusiastic journey, where you will accidently stumble upon the good life of savouring food, flavours, spices and exploring wines.

data.name: Karma Kasuri at Karma Haveli, Jaipur
data.description: Situated right in the middle of walled city of Jaipur, just 1 KM from City palace and Hawa mahal, Karma Kasuri at Karma Haveli in Jaipur by Karma Resorts is an authentic 1700s family mansion built in the golden age of the Maharajas. Designed and furnished by local Jaipur designers, there is an air of authenticity that surrounds this stunning location. Close to the ancient city walls, the Karma Haveli is a mere 10 minutes from the centre of Pink City. Karma Kasuri Restaurant serving mouthwatering cuisine, and a fully renovated ancient bawdi (stepped well) which forms the centre piece of the intimate gardens. Serves Rajasthani and North Indian Cuisine. Rajasthani delicacies like daal or meat-baati-churma, laal maans. Vegetarian and non-vegetarian thali options are also available. A perfect place for lunch kitty party, couple dinner kitty party or for small gathering like birthday parties.

data.name: Kitchen With A Cause
data.description: “An idea can change the world.” – Kitchen With A Cause is a firm believer of these valuable words. This restaurant started by few friends who were in the travel industry and wanted to do something different and better for society. Our kitchen offers a large menu of delicious dishes. But it’s not just about the food, it’s also about the cause behind it. Kitchen With A Cause provides certified paid internships to underprivileged young adults who have been rescued from the streets by NGOs. These individuals are trained in all aspects of running the operations of a restaurant. More importantly, we help these individuals build self-confidence and realize their potential. After the 6-month internship finishes, we help these young adults find permanent and rewarding jobs in the hospitality industry. We then welcome a new group of young adults to take their place. Our goal is to train as many young adults as possible and give these individuals a chance at a better future.
